name: Schrödinger's Cat (omniowl)
description:
A cute little game about a Cat that longs for more!

  • Art by Andreas Feldstedt
  • Design by Lani Feldstedt
  • Programming by Mads Sønderstrup
  • Sound & Music by Christoffer Krakou

Done in 2022 as a chill activity among friends. Not affiliated with any official jam.
